data.description:
Presenting a ready-to-move-in townhome, completed in 2021, featuring 3 bedrooms and 3 bathrooms. The main floor impresses with its open floor plan, welcoming an abundance of natural light, creating a spacious ambiance perfect for hosting gatherings. The modern kitchen is equipped with stainless steel appliances, quartz countertops, and a generously-sized island, ideal for both seating and additional preparation space. Upstairs, you'll find the primary bedroom, characterized by its airy feel, accompanied by a walk-in closet and an expansive ensuite bathroom. The Homeowners Association enhances the living experience with a chip card granting access to a wealth of amenities such as a pool, hot tub, clubhouse, playgrounds, fitness center, and sand volleyball court—all conveniently positioned at the front of the community. Benefit from the townhome's strategic location, providing easy access to shopping and a nearby light rail stop. If you're in search of a low-maintenance lifestyle, your quest ends here!

2.75% ASSUMABLE LOAN AVAILABLE!!! TAKE ADVANTAGE OF THE LOW RATE! 
If you  CAN NOT qualify for the ASSUMPTION - this property is qualified for a Community Reinvestment Program, Lender's Credit of 2.5% toward closing cost fees or Buying Rate Down.
